results.name: Square array (8 X 8) read by rows.
comment: Permutation contributing to the determinant that gives the 8th value of the Möbius function. Determinant of matrix is equal to 1. The array is asymmetrical.
link: Herbert S. Wilf, The Redheffer matrix of a partially ordered set, arXiv:math/0408263 [math.CO], 2004.
